Package: odkmerge
Type: Package
Title: Merge and Flatten ODK and KoboToolbox Repeat-Group Exports
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Kasim", "Chambulilo", email = "kassimchambulilo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools to read, detect, enrich, and merge repeat-group
    sheets produced by Open Data Kit (ODK) and KoboToolbox XLSForm exports.
    Automates the joining of parent and child sheets using standard ODK index
    columns, supports multi-level and nested repeat groups, and produces clean
    flat datasets ready for analysis.
